  "Description": {
    "English": "A <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">moderate</span> upgrade for the vessel's <span class=\"name name-technology\">pain suppression systems</span>. Use <VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><> to trigger node growth and begin the <VAL_ON>grafting process<>.<br><br>Each node is genetically unique, and exact upgrade statistics are <span class=\"name name-special\">unknown</span> until installation is complete.<br><br>Significantly improves <span class=\"name name-stellar\">living ship strength</span> for increased combat endurance.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "对飞船<span class=\"name name-technology\">疼痛抑制系统</span>的<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">普通</span>提升。使用<VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><>触发节点增长并开始<VAL_ON>嫁接过程<>。<br><br>每个节点在基因上都是独一无二的，具体升级信息在安装结束前<span class=\"name name-special\">未知</span>。<br><br>可显著提升<span class=\"name name-stellar\">船体强度</span>来提升战斗时的耐久度。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "太空船<span class=\"name name-technology\">疼痛抑制系統</span>的<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">一般</span>升級。用 <VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><> 觸發節點生長，並開始<VAL_ON>移植程序<>。<br><br>每個節點的基因皆不相同，直到安裝完成前，確切的升級數據為<span class=\"name name-special\">未知</span>。<br><br>顯著提升<span class=\"name name-stellar\">活體太空船強度</span>以便增加戰鬥持久力。"
  },
